### **Configuration Validation with Auto-Correction**
Extend [src/utils/config-validator.ts](mdc:src/utils/config-validator.ts):

```typescript
// Add new schema with auto-correction capabilities
const autoMaintainedComponentSchema = Joi.object({
  enabled: Joi.boolean().default(true),
  autoUpdate: Joi.boolean().default(true), // Enable automatic updates
  gitOpsIntegration: Joi.boolean().default(true), // Enable GitOps workflows
  monitoring: Joi.object({
    enabled: Joi.boolean().default(true),
    alerting: Joi.boolean().default(true),
    autoHealing: Joi.boolean().default(true)
