  }),
}).meta({
  description: 'Configuration for auto-maintained component',
  research: [
    'https://joi.dev/api/?v=17.7.0',
    'https://github.com/sideway/joi/blob/master/API.md'
  ],
  autoMaintenance: [
    'Configuration validates automatically on load',
    'Invalid values auto-corrected to safe defaults',
    'Schema migrations handled automatically'
  ]
});
```

