### **Feature Flags with GitOps Integration**
Use environment variables and Git-driven configuration for gradual rollout:

```typescript
// Feature flag pattern with GitOps integration
const FEATURE_AUTO_HEALING = process.env.FEATURE_AUTO_HEALING === 'true';
const FEATURE_ADVANCED_MONITORING = process.env.FEATURE_ADVANCED_MONITORING === 'true';

// GitOps-driven feature configuration
const featureConfig = await readGitOpsConfig('features/enabled-features.yaml');

if (FEATURE_AUTO_HEALING || featureConfig.autoHealing) {
  // Enable auto-healing components
  enableAutoHealingComponents();
}
```

